{"tid":114264,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無興趣入黎玩個遊戲？","createTime":"2017-02-09T15:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T18:10:48.000Z","uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93c38d70e87dad69f71a3fdf7fa670bc785eddb6","tid":114264,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:26:25.000Z","msg":"遊戲玩法：<br />\n在限定時段入黎留名（請順序留名）<br />\ne.g  1.樂極生悲殺人夜<br />\n<br />\n有一定人數之後就由我抽個數字出黎<br />\n抽中巴/絲打 就係挑戰方<br />\n<br />\n而挑戰方可以做一樣動作要去挑一個其中三位有留名既巴/絲，睇佢地挑唔挑戰到，做唔到既懲罰就係挑戰方可以要求果三位挑戰唔到既巴/絲打改佢想改既名<br />\n<br />\n規則：唔可以做犯法/危險野，唔可以要求做1 d會自爆野<br />\n<br />\n截止留名為2月10號11：59分<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就留名，無興趣就由佢沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7652905c76de58ede655791ede1ae18625fa83","tid":114264,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:29:35.000Z","msg":"留名睇沉"},{"pid":"1b82ff81436a49a528cf4bc077270a806c5f36bd","tid":114264,"uid":82006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇沉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好啦"},{"pid":"713bb67d364ea5484b6596fa22cbc8e49d09c659","tid":114264,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇沉</blockquote><br />\n留名睇沉"},{"pid":"a2e6fe839776a7b8e5a1fff025b319acd8265c3b","tid":114264,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名睇沉</blockquote><br />\n留名睇沉</blockquote><br />\n留名睇沉"},{"pid":"012c77282bd249761ba7afb16a27470f6b3ec461","tid":114264,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4970d4814e51cf6f9290caa6308511450a5f2f","tid":114264,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T02:24:37.0